'''圣母圣心堂'''（Our Lady of the Sacred Heart Church (OLSH) 替代翻译:圣心教堂圣母）是一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]教堂，位于澳大利亚新南威尔士州[[蘭域_(新南威爾士州)|蘭域]]（[[悉尼|悉尼]]东郊）Avoca 街，毗邻该区商业中心。该堂为[[哥特复兴式|哥特复兴式]]建筑，建于1888年。[[祭台|祭台]]附近有一[[哥特式|哥特式]]八角形[[小堂|小堂]]<ref>Sydney Architecture, John Haskell, UNSW Press (1997) p.81</ref>。字面名称翻译”我们的处女母亲，耶穌聖心”. 

该堂被列入遗产名录<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.environment.nsw.gov.au/heritageapp/ViewHeritageItemDetails.aspx?ID=2310074 |title=State Heritage Register |accessdate=2015-02-06 |archive-date=2018-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730140328/http://www.environment.nsw.gov.au/heritageapp/ViewHeritageItemDetails.aspx?ID=2310074 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，毗邻的砂岩建筑属于教堂所有，建于1870年，曾是市长住所，亦列入遗产名录<ref>[http://www.heritage.nsw.gov.au/07_subnav_01_2.cfm?itemid=2310074 State Heritage List]{{Dead link|date=2020年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

该堂区附设两所中学，两所小学<ref>[http://www.sacredheart.org.au Our Lady of the Sacred Heart Parish and St Margaret Mary’s - Randwick Parishes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacredheart.org.au/ |date=20201124212605 }} , ''[http://www.sacredheart.org.au/mission.html Mission Statement] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacredheart.org.au/mission.html |date=20200308045750 }}'', May, 2009.</ref>。

